pullRequest.title: Worldgen Mappings
pullRequest.bodyText: This PR improves FoliagePlacer mappings, SurfaceBuilder mappings, and a lot of general method names and parameter names. It also adds some javadoc to FoliagePlacers, as they are rather complicated to understand.
